data.text: Wowza! I Just found out from L that @andylassner  Jeannie and @portiaderossi were with you too Ellen and Taylor
During this #nightmare of a reality we are living if even a portion of this wonderful dream could come true...

For the night when someone knocked on my van window and the two of you were outside our van! We screamed and struggled to get out of our blankets for hugs. After a while we all went over to Breka Bakery and enjoyed sweets and each others company
